1
00:00:01,799 --> 00:00:06,000
You bastard! Let go!
I said, let go of me!

2
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:10,000
You are under arrest under the edict
of the Deviant Reformation Act!

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Now walk, deviant!

4
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:16,200
Me, a "deviant"!?
I’m just a normal human, goddammit!

5
00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:18,500
Let go of me, you bastard!
Let go!

6
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:20,200
Hmph! This brat!

7
00:00:20,200 --> 00:00:24,500
I heard that you’re from a famous family of knights,
but now you’re nothing but a mere delinquent!

8
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:26,299
Shut up!
That’s none of your business!

9
00:00:26,299 --> 00:00:27,299
Let go of me!

10
00:00:27,299 --> 00:00:30,000
For a kid you sure are strong, but...

11
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:33,500
...it seems that you haven’t fully awakened yet.

12
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:36,000
Now, cut it out and turn yourself in.

13
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,500
Let’s go!

